<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Essential Chart supports the <Bold>Doughnut Chart </Bold> type. In this demo, series displayed in Doughnut chart type with its data labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Segments can be shown with different interior colors by enabling the <Bold>ColorEach</Bold> property of ChartSeries.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to apply palette for ChartArea.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Index"</Bold> helps to change inner radius of the doughnut.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Explode All"</Bold> helps to explode all the segments in the doughnut </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Enable Effects"</Bold> helps to apply effects to the doughnut. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Index"</Bold> helps to select a segment to be exploded</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Explode Radius"</Bold> helps to select the radius of an exploded segment</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"ShowDataLabels"</Bold> sets the visibility of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>

</FlowDocument>
